com.nestedbird.modules.sitemap

Class SitemapGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.nestedbird.modules.sitemap.SitemapGenerator

  • public class SitemapGenerator
extends java.lang.Object
    This generates a sitemap for the websites major resources. I dont want to bother with actually using a POJO to XML system because of how much of a pain and a headache XML can be. So i am just manually creating it with strings.
